<p>i am trying to use structure pointer of C in lua .</p>  <pre><code>    #include &lt;stdio.h&gt;      struct name     {        int a;        float b;     };      int main()     {         struct name *ptr,p;         ptr=&amp;p;            /* Referencing pointer to memory address of p */         printf("Enter integer: ");         scanf("%d",&amp;(*ptr).a);         printf("%d%f",(*ptr).a,ptr-&gt;a);         return 0;     } </code></pre>  <p>How to write (*ptr).a or ptr->a in Lua?</p>